'''飓风洛伦佐'''（{{lang-en|Hurricane Lorenzo}}）是2007年9月下旬经[[快速增强|快速发展]]后袭击墨西哥[[韦拉克鲁斯州|韦拉克鲁斯州]]的一个[[热带气旋|热带气旋]]，也是[[2007年大西洋飓风季|2007年大西洋飓风季]]第12场获得命名的风暴和第5场飓风。系统由[[东风波|东风波]]在[[墨西哥湾|墨西哥湾]]西南部形成，经过两天的蜿蜒行进并且没有出现发展后，系统开始稳步西进，组织结构也有改善。短短18小时里，气旋风速从每小时55公里提高到130公里，即从热带低气压跃升为飓风。9月28日，洛伦佐在[[飓风迪安|飓风迪安]]过去仅1个月后从韦拉克鲁斯州科卢特拉附近[[登陆_(气象学)|登陆]]，然后在陆地上空迅速消散。

韦拉克鲁斯州受这场飓风影响最为严重，损失总额超过10亿[[墨西哥比索|墨西哥比索]]（相当于同年的9200万[[美元|美元]]），其中大部分是该州北部的道路受损，另有数百幢房屋遭到破坏。韦拉克鲁斯州和邻近的[[伊达尔戈州|伊达尔戈州]]共有112个[[自治区_(墨西哥)|自治区]]的12万3320人受灾，整个墨西哥共有6人丧生，其中韦拉克鲁斯州1人，[[普埃布拉州|普埃布拉州]]5人，这5人中包括因山体滑坡遇难的一家三口。

== 气象历史 ==
{{storm path|Lorenzo 2007 track.png}}
9月11日，一股[[东风波|东风波]]离开非洲西海岸。经过热带大西洋后，东风波又穿越大半个[[加勒比海|加勒比海]]，于9月21日发展出[[雷暴|雷暴]]区。<ref name="tcr">{{cite report | author = James Franklin | date = 2007-10-18 | title = Hurricane Lorenzo Tropical Cyclone Report | accessdate = 2015-12-05 | publisher = National Hurricane Center | deadurl = no | archiveurl = https://web.archive.org/web/20151011103107/http://www.nhc.noaa.gov/data/tcr/AL132007_Lorenzo.pdf | format = [[PDF|PDF]] | url = http://www.nhc.noaa.gov/data/tcr/AL132007_Lorenzo.pdf | archivedate = 2015-10-11}}</ref>接下来系统出现分裂，其北部经过[[尤卡坦半岛|尤卡坦半岛]]后于9月23日发展出[[低气压|低气压区]]<ref name="tcr" /><ref>{{cite report | author1 = Knabb | author2 = Rhome | date = 2007-09-23 | title = Tropical Weather Outlook | publisher = [[国家飓风中心|National Hurricane Center]] | accessdate = 2011-05-12 | url = http://www.nhc.noaa.gov/archive/text/TWOAT/2007/TWOAT.200709230929.txt | format = TXT | archivedate = 2015-07-07 | deadurl = no | archiveurl = https://web.archive.org/web/20150707030719/http://www.nhc.noaa.gov/archive/text/TWOAT/2007/TWOAT.200709230929.txt}}</ref>。气象机构原计划派[[飓风猎人|飓风猎人]]侦察机飞入系统侦察，发现低气压区由于受到强烈[[风切变|风切变]]的不利影响而在墨西哥湾东南部上空变成杂乱无章<ref>{{cite report | author = Eric Brown | date = 2007-09-23 | title = Tropical Weather Outlook | publisher = National Hurricane Center | accessdate = 2015-12-05 | format = TXT | archivedate = 2012-10-25 | archiveurl = https://web.archive.org/web/20121025125423/http://www.nhc.noaa.gov/archive/text/TWOAT/2007/TWOAT.200709232129.txt | url = http://www.nhc.noaa.gov/archive/text/TWOAT/2007/TWOAT.200709232129.txt | deadurl = no}}</ref>。不过，风切变接下来有所减退<ref name="tcr" />，9月25日晚，另一架飓风猎人发现系统已发展出闭合下层[[大气环流|环流]]。根据这一观测结果，结合雷暴活动的持续存在，[[国家飓风中心|美国国家飓风中心]]将位于[[塔毛利帕斯州|塔毛利帕斯州]][[坦皮科|坦皮科]]以东给305公里的系统归类为第十三号热带低气压<ref>{{cite report | author = James Franklin | date = 2007-09-26 | archiveurl = https://web.archive.org/web/20151002123020/http://www.nhc.noaa.gov/archive/2007/al13/al132007.discus.001.shtml | title = Tropical Depression Thirteen Special Discussion One | publisher = National Hurricane Center | accessdate = 2015-12-05 | url = http://www.nhc.noaa.gov/archive/2007/al13/al132007.discus.001.shtml? | archivedate = 2015-10-02 | deadurl = no}}</ref>。

由于所处海域存在弱转向气流，低气压在发展期间的行动方向很不规则，但总体保持南下趋势，其移动路线在形成阶段呈小规模环路<ref name="tcr" />。接下来，气旋行经洋面水温有明显提高，风切变也逐渐减少，系统的[[对流|对流]]逐渐组织，但风速提升相对缓慢<ref>{{cite report | author = Erick Pasch | date = 2007-09-27 | title = Tropical Depression Thirteen Discussion Five | publisher = National Hurricane Center | accessdate = 2015-12-05 | archivedate = 2015-10-02 | archiveurl = https://web.archive.org/web/20151002123033/http://www.nhc.noaa.gov/archive/2007/al13/al132007.discus.005.shtml | url = http://www.nhc.noaa.gov/archive/2007/al13/al132007.discus.005.shtml? | deadurl = no}}</ref>。系统上空有[[反气旋|反气旋]]形成，低气压也于[[协调世界时|协调世界时]]9朋27日中午12点左右在[[韦拉克鲁斯州|韦拉克鲁斯州]][[图斯潘_(韦拉克鲁斯州)|图斯潘]]以东约240公里海域升级成热带风暴并获名“洛伦佐”（{{lang|en|Lorenzo}}），并因东面有[[高压脊|高压脊]]而稳步向西前进。随着风暴逐渐逼近陆地，洛伦佐突然意外[[快速增强|急剧强化]]，在成为热带风暴不到12小时后就进一步增强成飓风。<ref name="tcr" />

雷达图像显示洛伦佐迅速发展出闭合[[风眼|风眼墙]]，气象机构估计飓风于{{lang|en|[[协调世界时|UTC]]}}9月28日凌晨0点左右达到[[最大持续风速|风力时速]]130公里的最高强度。气旋中心有强劲且对称的对流保持，但其结构在{{lang|en|UTC}}当天早上5点以风速每小时约120公里强度从韦拉克鲁斯州科卢特拉附近登岸前略有恶化<ref name="tcr" /><ref>{{cite report | author = James Franklin | date = 2007-09-28 | title = Hurricane Lorenzo Discussion Eleven | publisher = National Hurricane Center | accessdate = 2011-05-12 | archiveurl = https://web.archive.org/web/20151002123053/http://www.nhc.noaa.gov/archive/2007/al13/al132007.discus.011.shtml | deadurl = no | url = http://www.nhc.noaa.gov/archive/2007/al13/al132007.discus.011.shtml? | archivedate = 2015-10-02}}</ref>。风暴强度在登陆后很快降低到热带低气压水平<ref name="tcr" />并逐渐向内陆前进，对流逐渐退化，在海岸沿线形成[[雨带|雨带]]，环流也因此变得难以辨别<ref>{{cite report | author = Lixion Avila | date = 2007-09-28 | title = Tropical Depression Lorenzo Discussion Thirteen | publisher = National Hurricane Center | accessdate = 2015-12-05 | archivedate = 2015-10-02 | archiveurl = https://web.archive.org/web/20151002123115/http://www.nhc.noaa.gov/archive/2007/al13/al132007.discus.013.shtml | url = http://www.nhc.noaa.gov/archive/2007/al13/al132007.discus.013.shtml? | deadurl = no}}</ref>。登陆仅19小时后，洛伦佐的环流就完全消散，不再属热带气旋<ref name="tcr" />。

== 防灾措施和影响 ==
洛伦佐登陆约26小时前，墨西哥政府向韦拉克鲁斯州帕尔马索拉（{{lang|en|Palma Sola}}）到拉克鲁斯（{{lang|en|La Cruz}}）之间地区发布[[热带气旋警告|热带风暴观察预警]]。风暴登陆前约14小时，帕尔马索拉到卡沃罗霍（{{lang|en|Cabo Rojo}}）之间地区接获热带风暴警告，并在6小时后升级成飓风警告。<ref name="tcr" />墨西哥民防官员宣布韦拉克鲁斯州大部分地区进入“红色警戒”状态<ref>{{cite news | agency = [[新华社|新华社]] | title = Mexico issues "red alert" against tropical storm Lorenzo | year = 2007 | publisher = People's Daily Online | accessdate = 2015-12-05 | archiveurl = https://web.archive.org/web/20151001123849/http://en.people.cn/90001/90782/91341/6273439.html | deadurl = no | url = http://en.people.cn/90001/90782/91341/6273439.html | archivedate = 2015-10-01}}</ref>。官员下令该州沿海地区的学校停课<ref>{{cite news | author = Catherine Bremer | title = Hurricane Lorenzo lashes Mexican Gulf coast | publisher = Reuters | accessdate = 2015-12-05 | url = http://in.reuters.com/article/idINIndia-29757120070928 | date = 2007-09-28 | archiveurl = https://web.archive.org/web/20110523122625/http://in.reuters.com/article/worldNews/idINIndia-29757120070928 | deadurl = no | archivedate = 2011-05-23}}</ref>，科卢特拉港、图斯潘港和瑙特拉港被迫关闭<ref>{{cite news | agency = [[美联社|Associated Press]] | title = Lorenzo becomes hurricane off Mexico | year = 2007 | publisher = ''The Tehran Times'' | accessdate = 2015-12-05 | url = http://www.tehrantimes.com/index_View.asp?code=153928 | archive-date = 2015-09-29 | archive-url = https://web.archive.org/web/20150929190042/http://www.tehrantimes.com/index_View.asp?code=153928 | dead-url = no }}</ref>。韦拉克鲁斯州共开设有315个避难所，相邻的[[伊达尔戈州|伊达尔戈州]]也开设了6个，风暴期间一共有4万5164人前来躲避<ref name="wmo">{{cite web | author1 = Michel Rosengaus | author2 = Alberto Hernández Unzón | year = 2007 | publisher = World Meteorological Organization | title = Informe de México sobre la Temporada de Huracanes 2007 e Inundaciones Asocidas | accessdate = 2015-12-05 | url = http://www.wmo.int/pages/prog/www/tcp/Meetings/HC30/documents/MEXICO.pdf | format = PDF | archive-date = 2016-03-04 | archive-url = https://web.archive.org/web/20160304055242/http://www.wmo.int/pages/prog/www/tcp/Meetings/HC30/documents/MEXICO.pdf | dead-url = no }}</ref>，韦拉克鲁斯州政府还提供巴士将居民从家中接到避难所<ref name="eu928b">{{cite news | newspaper = El Universal | date = 2007-09-28 | title = Causa Lorenzo severas afectaciones en Veracruz | accessdate = 2015-12-05 | url = http://archivo.eluniversal.com.mx/notas/451857.html | archive-date = 2021-04-03 | archive-url = https://web.archive.org/web/20210403072817/https://archivo.eluniversal.com.mx/notas/451857.html | dead-url = no }}</ref>。洛伦佐形成后，出于对风暴影响墨西哥湾石油开采设施的担忧，天然气价格出现上涨<ref>{{cite web | author = Elaine Frei | date = 2007-09-27 | title = WTI, Brent each add over $2 per barrel | publisher = Investment Markets | accessdate = 2015-12-05 | url = http://www.investmentmarkets.co.uk/20070927-969.html | archive-date = 2015-09-29 | archive-url = https://web.archive.org/web/20150929223430/http://www.investmentmarkets.co.uk/20070927-969.html | dead-url = no }}</ref>。

飓风洛伦佐登陆韦拉克鲁斯直接影响的地区在仅1个月前才受到[[飓风迪安|飓风迪安]]重创。受洛伦佐影响的主要是沿海小渔村，还有多条输电线缆因狂风中断<ref name="td">{{cite news | author = Staff Writer | newspaper = Times Daily | title = Lorenzo batters Mexican coastline | date = 2007-09-27 | accessdate = 2015-12-05 | url = https://news.google.com/newspapers?id=YYQ0AAAAIBAJ&sjid=H8cEAAAAIBAJ&pg=4956,3851577&dq=mexico+lorenzo+dean&hl=en | archive-date = 2021-04-03 | archive-url = https://web.archive.org/web/20210403072810/https://news.google.com/newspapers?id=YYQ0AAAAIBAJ&sjid=H8cEAAAAIBAJ&pg=4956%2C3851577&dq=mexico+lorenzo+dean&hl=en | dead-url = no }}</ref>，导致约8万5000人失去供电<ref name="eu928">{{cite news | newspaper = El Universal | date = 2007-09-28 | title = Suman cuatro muertos por paso de Lorenzo en México | accessdate = 2015-12-05 | url = http://archivo.eluniversal.com.mx/notas/451911.html | archive-date = 2021-04-03 | archive-url = https://web.archive.org/web/20210403072752/https://archivo.eluniversal.com.mx/notas/451911.html | dead-url = no }}</ref>。为防止中断的电缆引发触电事故，官员将韦拉克鲁斯州北部多个自治区的电网切断<ref name="eu928b" />。狂风还摧毁了瑙特拉许多房屋的屋顶<ref name="tcr" />。洛伦佐还在沿海及更加内陆的地区产生暴雨，最高降雨量达326毫米。这些降水引起山洪爆发和[[泥石流|泥石流]]，夺走至少4条人命<ref name="tcr" />，其中包括[[普埃布拉州|普埃布拉州]]的一家三口<ref name="td" />，另有3条高速公路因山体滑坡导致部分路段封闭<ref name="eu928" />，部分地区的洪水有约30厘米深<ref name="eu928b" />。狂风暴雨共同影响，导致普埃布拉州169套房屋受损，[[伊达尔戈州|伊达尔戈州]]的[[圣洛伦佐河_(墨西哥)|圣洛伦佐河]]泛滥，迫使200余人撤离<ref name="tcr" />。韦拉克鲁斯州也有多条河流泛滥，导致约2万5000人离开家园。[[卡索内斯河|卡索内斯河]]沿线有上千幢房屋被淹，当地警方协助居民疏散<ref name="eu928" />。估计韦拉克鲁斯州一共遭受了价值10亿[[墨西哥比索|墨西哥比索]]（相当于同年的9200万[[美元|美元]]）的破坏<ref name="lev">{{cite web |author=Lev García |date=2007-10-02 |title='Lorenzo' deja daños por mil millones de pesos en Veracruz |publisher=El Mañana |archiveurl=https://archive.is/20130221042014/http://www.elmanana.com.mx/notas.asp?id=19035 |accessdate=2013-02-21 |url=http://www.elmanana.com.mx/notas.asp?id=19035 |deadurl=yes |archivedate=2013-02-21 }}</ref>，其中大部分是该州北部的道路受损<ref name="lj" />。

总体而计，这场飓风共对韦拉克鲁斯州和伊达尔戈州的12万3320人造成影响，促使112个[[自治区_(墨西哥)|自治区]]进入紧急状态<ref name="wmo" />，以便灾民获取应急物资<ref>{{cite web | author = Notimex | publisher = El Universal | date = 2007-09-28 | title = Declaran emergencia en 92 municipios de Veracruz por Lorenzo | accessdate = 2015-12-05 | url = http://archivo.eluniversal.com.mx/notas/451941.html | archive-date = 2021-04-03 | archive-url = https://web.archive.org/web/20210403072914/https://archivo.eluniversal.com.mx/notas/451941.html | dead-url = no }}</ref>。墨西哥共有6人遇难，其中普埃布拉州占5人<ref name="wmo" />。气旋过去3天后，所有学校已重新开放<ref name="lev" />。墨西哥政府向韦拉克鲁斯州受灾最严重的地区送去食品、饮用水和建筑材料<ref name="lj">{{cite web |author=Staff Writer |publisher=La Journada |date=2007-10-04 |title=Cien ataúdes, ayuda federal a damnificados de Veracruz |accessdate=2015-12-05 |archiveurl=https://archive.is/20130221030911/http://www.jornada.unam.mx/2007/10/04/index.php?section=estados&article=036n1est |url=http://www.jornada.unam.mx/2007/10/04/index.php?section=estados&article=036n1est |deadurl=no |archivedate=2013-02-21 }}</ref>。风暴过去后，约有500名电力工人被派往韦拉克鲁斯州灾区恢复供电<ref name="eu928" />。

